title: zhzz
author: zhzz
content: My accounts are getting banned due to subscriber service purchases. I need an account with a couple (min. 3 digit, best case 5 digit sub count) of subscribers.Anyone here wanting to sell an old YouTube channel? best would be already monetized.

comments.author: MB boss
comments.body: I sent you a personal message with details of three YouTube channels. There is my telegram username, you can contact there too. Thanks
